{"tid":145014,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"關於華沙機場轉機","createTime":"2017-03-06T02:03:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-06T03:53:46.000Z","uid":12755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c0d040fbdc1fa48187c03677447caa54aea7e84a","tid":145014,"uid":12755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T02:03:55.000Z","msg":"krakow飛華沙機場轉機去莫斯科，但中間只有一個鐘，其實夠唔夠時間？唔該曬各位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2523ad39f6d239ddebcbd563ffdcd4b882edd9d","tid":145014,"uid":57460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T02:06:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>krakow飛華沙機場轉機去莫斯科，但中間只有一個鐘，其實夠唔夠時間？唔該曬各位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果係airline官網買佢畀你買佢就會guarantee咗得，唔係佢要補返機位畀你。"},{"pid":"f7df42bbe17051bee7f15171d80d2f6970d04124","tid":145014,"uid":12755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T02:19:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>krakow飛華沙機場轉機去莫斯科，但中間只有一個鐘，其實夠唔夠時間？唔該曬各位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果係airline官網買佢畀你買佢就會guarantee咗得，唔係佢要補返機位畀你。</blockquote><br />\n咁様，但我驚如果萬一下班機要等幾個鐘咪奶野，因為我去到莫斯科svo機場過幾個鐘搭機番香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5987dc09f567235a25ed065084cfe30ad9aadd0c","tid":145014,"uid":26937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T02:22:57.000Z","msg":"以香港既做法係<br />\n夠一個鐘就可以做到轉機<br />\n至於趕唔切要補就要睇你條飛點買"},{"pid":"1c1266b4fcb6b8deb652e698d5878da447db0e0e","tid":145014,"uid":12755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T02:48:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以香港既做法係<br />\n夠一個鐘就可以做到轉機<br />\n至於趕唔切要補就要睇你條飛點買</blockquote><br />\n條飛點買？諗住上俄航官網買，但其實我諗華沙機場唔太大應該1個鐘ok但係華沙飛莫斯科係國際線wo，使唔使要提前之類？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未試過轉機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> thx巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0efb7e6f3ff80eb96ef96f6be560e945260ad894","tid":145014,"uid":26937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T02:53:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以香港既做法係<br />\n夠一個鐘就可以做到轉機<br />\n至於趕唔切要補就要睇你條飛點買</blockquote><br />\n條飛點買？諗住上俄航官網買，但其實我諗華沙機場唔太大應該1個鐘ok但係華沙飛莫斯科係國際線wo，使唔使要提前之類？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未試過轉機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> thx巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正路你係官網買<br />\n佢出到兩程比你<br />\n佢會show埋d departure time<br />\n其實已經可以轉到機 <br />\n只不過到時落到機靠自己搵路"},{"pid":"1298a2496df72d7468cb763f9f92e446619ba06e","tid":145014,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T02:54:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以香港既做法係<br />\n夠一個鐘就可以做到轉機<br />\n至於趕唔切要補就要睇你條飛點買</blockquote><br />\n條飛點買？諗住上俄航官網買，但其實我諗華沙機場唔太大應該1個鐘ok但係華沙飛莫斯科係國際線wo，使唔使要提前之類？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未試過轉機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> thx巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你飛SVO 果程機可以直掛行李去香港，但係登機牌要去到SVO先再出俾你。"},{"pid":"bdca645b90299f2b999c8dc525adf8b2b3183468","tid":145014,"uid":71605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:05:05.000Z","msg":"krakow飛華沙笑撚左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔搭火車?"},{"pid":"329cd4b202df1c35f1891524431c61d63e04ff0e","tid":145014,"uid":12755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:19:15.000Z","msg":"自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇錯原來係波蘭航空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be8d0269338ff27554d4872543b00046f9c30714","tid":145014,"uid":12755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:19:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>krakow飛華沙笑撚左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔搭火車?</blockquote><br />\n有乜出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69199481efa6cfea0eddc75d77f27d09b9f33e73","tid":145014,"uid":12755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:20:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>以香港既做法係<br />\n夠一個鐘就可以做到轉機<br />\n至於趕唔切要補就要睇你條飛點買</blockquote><br />\n條飛點買？諗住上俄航官網買，但其實我諗華沙機場唔太大應該1個鐘ok但係華沙飛莫斯科係國際線wo，使唔使要提前之類？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未試過轉機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> thx巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你飛SVO 果程機可以直掛行李去香港，但係登機牌要去到SVO先再出俾你。</blockquote><br />\n直掛未試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cf8720ffbc363f068d080a172e01e5adfb4c823","tid":145014,"uid":12755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:22:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>以香港既做法係<br />\n夠一個鐘就可以做到轉機<br />\n至於趕唔切要補就要睇你條飛點買</blockquote><br />\n條飛點買？諗住上俄航官網買，但其實我諗華沙機場唔太大應該1個鐘ok但係華沙飛莫斯科係國際線wo，使唔使要提前之類？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未試過轉機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> thx巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正路你係官網買<br />\n佢出到兩程比你<br />\n佢會show埋d departure time<br />\n其實已經可以轉到機 <br />\n只不過到時落到機靠自己搵路</blockquote><br />\n機場唔大搵路應該唔難，但我唔肯定一個鐘其實係咪真係ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7fa16f859c1d4af1379f3cb07f09bfa03d86fb1","tid":145014,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:24:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>以香港既做法係<br />\n夠一個鐘就可以做到轉機<br />\n至於趕唔切要補就要睇你條飛點買</blockquote><br />\n條飛點買？諗住上俄航官網買，但其實我諗華沙機場唔太大應該1個鐘ok但係華沙飛莫斯科係國際線wo，使唔使要提前之類？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未試過轉機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> thx巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你飛SVO 果程機可以直掛行李去香港，但係登機牌要去到SVO先再出俾你。</blockquote><br />\n直掛未試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要你由華沙去香港都係俄航同一張單買先有得直掛。<br />\n<br />\n同埋俄航都幾痴線下，極短時間轉機都可以一次過買，都唔驚有阻滯。"},{"pid":"66d87d4fcd671c72a64f97daaf7e73ca637ccccb","tid":145014,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:26:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>以香港既做法係<br />\n夠一個鐘就可以做到轉機<br />\n至於趕唔切要補就要睇你條飛點買</blockquote><br />\n條飛點買？諗住上俄航官網買，但其實我諗華沙機場唔太大應該1個鐘ok但係華沙飛莫斯科係國際線wo，使唔使要提前之類？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未試過轉機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> thx巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正路你係官網買<br />\n佢出到兩程比你<br />\n佢會show埋d departure time<br />\n其實已經可以轉到機 <br />\n只不過到時落到機靠自己搵路</blockquote><br />\n機場唔大搵路應該唔難，但我唔肯定一個鐘其實係咪真係ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你其他航空公司轉俄航，俄航唔會包你有咩DELAY 上唔到機。<br />\n<br />\n你第一班一遲就死，自己諗。<br />\n<br />\n或者你得閒無事做睇下 FlightAware 統計下第一班機準唔準時。"},{"pid":"07fc95fe11352c06cf5b3dbecca74dca5ce42457","tid":145014,"uid":12755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:48:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>以香港既做法係<br />\n夠一個鐘就可以做到轉機<br />\n至於趕唔切要補就要睇你條飛點買</blockquote><br />\n條飛點買？諗住上俄航官網買，但其實我諗華沙機場唔太大應該1個鐘ok但係華沙飛莫斯科係國際線wo，使唔使要提前之類？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未試過轉機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> thx巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正路你係官網買<br />\n佢出到兩程比你<br />\n佢會show埋d departure time<br />\n其實已經可以轉到機 <br />\n只不過到時落到機靠自己搵路</blockquote><br />\n機場唔大搵路應該唔難，但我唔肯定一個鐘其實係咪真係ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你其他航空公司轉俄航，俄航唔會包你有咩DELAY 上唔到機。<br />\n<br />\n你第一班一遲就死，自己諗。<br />\n<br />\n或者你得閒無事做睇下 FlightAware 統計下第一班機準唔準時。</blockquote><br />\n唔該曬巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再度一度先"},{"pid":"82cc7af8d316bdcd77af0d4cac028c3c85ca19e9","tid":145014,"uid":51348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:51:04.000Z","msg":"華沙機埸好撚細"},{"pid":"afb287290f24669338d1d190c8a2d348ccebb41d","tid":145014,"uid":12755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:52:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>以香港既做法係<br />\n夠一個鐘就可以做到轉機<br />\n至於趕唔切要補就要睇你條飛點買</blockquote><br />\n條飛點買？諗住上俄航官網買，但其實我諗華沙機場唔太大應該1個鐘ok但係華沙飛莫斯科係國際線wo，使唔使要提前之類？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未試過轉機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> thx巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你飛SVO 果程機可以直掛行李去香港，但係登機牌要去到SVO先再出俾你。</blockquote><br />\n直掛未試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要你由華沙去香港都係俄航同一張單買先有得直掛。<br />\n<br />\n同埋俄航都幾痴線下，極短時間轉機都可以一次過買，都唔驚有阻滯。</blockquote><br />\n睇錯原來係Polandair<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實如果上到機去到莫斯科先係3點，但我8點飛番香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07e649c3c2222c9f4743c34ef66f7485b815a3f7","tid":145014,"uid":57460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:53:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>krakow飛華沙笑撚左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔搭火車?</blockquote><br />\n有乜出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都試過喺WAW轉機去KRK，<br />\n唔知有咩咁好笑。"}]}